    ( S Z ) .

% Verifying that 3 squared is 9
test-exp = eqnat ( exp ( S ( S ( S Z ) ) ) ( S ( S Z ) ) ) ( S ( S ( S ( S ( S ( S ( S ( S ( S Z ) ) ) ) ) ) ) ) ) !
